# UI Consistency

Use CSS variables from `:root` — never hardcode new hex colors in HTML/CSS except confetti.

| Token | Use |
|-------|-----|
| `--green` | Primary CTA, active date tab, completed calendar |
| `--surface` / `--surface-2` | Cards vs inputs/rows |
| `--muted` | Secondary text |

Components:
- Buttons: `.primary` / `.secondary` (pill, 56px min-height)
- Cards: `.panel`, `.exercise-card` (8px radius, 22px padding)
- Labels: `.eyebrow` above headings
- Lists: `.set-row` (3-col grid), `.badge` for tags

Layout: `.app-shell` max 960px; bottom `.bottom-appbar` fixed — leave 112px bottom padding on main content.

New screens: match existing SVG icon style (24×24, stroke 2.2, round caps). Profile flows go in `#profileDrawer` sub-views.
